						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> by a <hi rend="italic">vēḷāṉ</hi> by name Kōdaṉdaṉ of Śīkaranallūr in kuṉṟiśūḻ-nāḍu, a division of Raṭṭapāḍikoṇdaśōḻa-vaḷanāḍu, to the temple of Trivikrama-Chōḷīśvaramuḍaiya-Mahādēva at Mēlmaṇinallūr, with one Kōvaṉ Śōḻan as a permanent tenant paying the <hi rend="italic">kuḍimai-kīḻiṟai</hi> thereon.</p>						

						</summary>
